ate": "2026-02-12 11:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857922431,45974302,1474]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63242283]evelin3[/uid] (2026-02-12 11:26):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大请问恒科怎么看呢？[/quote]<br/>不看 有钱去做过年多出来那几天而已  但是主战场还是大A 我觉得没必要去", "lou": 801, "content_length": 68, "reply_to": 857922431, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770866907}, {"pid": 857922837, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 11:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857922760,45974302,1474]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61649350]FutureMax002[/uid] (2026-02-12 11:28):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，这是不是也是提前复盘做好预案，提前做好涨什么板块-买哪只股票-什么时候买卖的预案[s:a2:不明觉厉][/quote]<br/>你这不是废话么  我前面不是带过复盘了？", "lou": 802, "content_length": 41, "reply_to": 857922760, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770866971}, {"pid": 857923156, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 89, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 11:31", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "节前红包都吃到了吧  好好过年吧 <br/>哪个前几天叫你们4000点清仓过年的 记得敲他闷棍然后拉黑他", "lou": 803, "content_length": 82, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770867117}, {"pid": 857928568, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 24, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 12:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857926593,45974302,1478]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60175320]asdfzywzyw[/uid] (2026-02-12 11:55):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，您之前推荐的那本交易心理学已经快看完了，想过年再充实一下自己，求再推荐一些书，谢谢！[/quote]<br/><br/>我也不是看书做起来的", "lou": 804, "content_length": 25, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 857926593, "postdatetimestamp": 1770869456}, {"pid": 857933192, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 40, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 12:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857931235,45974302,1480]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-02-12 12:33):[/b]<br/><br/>昨天狼大说不做卫星了，我就寻思把仓位切到哪，我看了东方电气，昨天缩量十字星，本来想买这个的，最后还是选择了机器人，今天一看东方电气涨停了[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202602/12/jmQ1aw-4dehKsT3cSlj-5e.jpg[/img]<br/>噢 你前面问为什么不做卫星是吧 忘记回了 因为十字星后第二天没有突破，上面卖单一点没撤 还加大了 就是等看谁进去帮他解放的样子<br/>然后板块没有带动效应，巨力那种是单独的赌海上回收的绳索，我说的是发动机和卫星都没有一个起高的 ，所以就撤了<br/>然后带他们去玩石油去了。", "lou": 805, "content_length": 287, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202602/12/jmQ1aw-4dehKsT3cSlj-5e.jpg", "size": 28, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202602/12", "name": "jmQ1aw-4dehKsT3cSlj-5e.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "120"}], "reply_to": 857931235, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770871826}, {"pid": 857933530, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 12:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "节前因为极度缩量 你们奢望半导体ETF能大涨就和看中继旭创能大涨一样没有道理，没那么多钱啊<br/>ETF大票不都一样<br/>但是细分很好啊，我觉得很好", "lou": 806, "content_length": 126, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770872019}, {"pid": 857934030, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 12:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857933814,45974302,1481]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67086272]冷酷鸡腿堡game[/uid] (2026-02-12 12:56):[/b]<br/><br/>味道纳米这种么<br/>越看越好看[/quote]<br/>光刻胶 MLCC IGBT这些我觉得目前都挺好  不过很多人没看到。这没办法 也是涨价逻辑", "lou": 807, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 857933814, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770872276}, {"pid": 857939121, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 13:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857938805,45974302,1484]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65367177]气运之茉[/uid] (2026-02-12 13:37):[/b]<br/><br/>这个走的应该是北美缺电，变压器SST后面可能会出货给xAI[/quote]<br/>不是啊。。做的是这段时间发酵的AI应用爆算力。。。你不见都是国内算力租赁么", "lou": 808, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 857938805, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770874845}, {"pid": 857939690, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 32, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 13:45", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857939465,45974302,1485]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67085379]小蝎子ICE3[/uid] (2026-02-12 13:43):[/b]<br/><br/>关键时刻到了<br/>按照我的预想<br/>散户出金上午没赚钱，会在下午刚刚回本或者微微赚钱的时候美滋滋的拿红包走人<br/>殊不知<br/>捡了芝麻[s:ac:哭笑][s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>中午之前发现指数回撤了 然后猛猛买了逆回购的 等下拍断第三条腿都么用", "lou": 809, "content_length": 69, "reply_to": 857939465, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770875118}, {"pid": 857940323, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 27, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 13:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857940048,45974302,1485]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60621194]HoshiZorA_Z[/uid] (2026-02-12 13:48):[/b]<br/><br/>今天液冷和AIDC、电力储能的红包发的恁爽，怕是都算准了散户这两天要跑路<br/>好多平时封板都困难的票今天都是嘎嘎猛<br/>没散户当藤壶就是爽[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>都是机构的超额方向  机构就是这么贱 你明知道过年有红包 但是就是弄到你怀疑自己的逻辑 然后走掉", "lou": 810, "content_length": 91, "reply_to": 857940048, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770875452}, {"pid": 857941416, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 14:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857940714,45974302,1485]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61649350]FutureMax002[/uid] (2026-02-12 13:54):[/b]<br/><br/>R001 -4了，都在逆回购[/quote]<br/>是啊。。我真是不理解 散户能有很多钱？然后扣掉手续费还有收益？这不是骗小白不懂么<br/>卖股票 收手续费  逆回购也要手续费  买回去股票不仅丧失先手 再卖还要一次手续费。。。", "lou": 811, "content_length": 159, "reply_to": 857940714, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770876020}, {"pid": 857941877, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 14:04", "subject": "", "a